description: This stunning condo is located in a fully renovated building in a prime South Boston spot, offering modern urban living. The open-concept design features a sleek kitchen with custom cabinets, stainless steel appliances by Thermador including a gas stove, built-in coffee station, and LED-lit open shelving. Beautiful stained wood floors flow throughout, and the primary suite includes a private, tiled bathroom with a luxurious multi-head shower. The custom-tiled main bathroom is equally impressive. Enjoy the convenience of wired ceiling speakers and controllers, plus a private balcony. This home is equipped with efficient forced-air gas heating, central AC, and on-demand tankless hot water. A garage parking spot is included. Just a short distance from shops, restaurants, parks, and the beach, this is South Boston living at its finest.
